    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(L) In Christi nomine breve recordationis qualiter in civitatem <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Consules">Luca prope porta Sancti
                            Fridiani</placeName>, presentia <rs key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines"
                            >bonorum hominum</rs> quorum nomina subter leguntur, <persName><name
                                ref="Brunectus">Brunectus</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Sigismundus">Sesmundellus</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Guericzus">Guerriscius</name></persName> germanis quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Rainuccius">Ranucci</name></persName>, pro se
                        ipsis et pro <persName><name ref="Rustichellus">Rusticello</name></persName>
                        germano eorum, per fustem quem in suis detinebant manibus, fecerunt finem et
                        refutationem et dationem et perdationem in manu <persName><name
                                ref="Ildebrandus">Ildebrandi</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Cariccio">Caricciori</name></persName>,
                        conversi <orgName key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs
                                key="#Hospitals">ospitalis</rs> de <placeName ref="#places/3207"
                                key="#Hospitals">Altopascio</placeName></orgName>, recipientem in
                        vice <persName><name ref="Wido">Guidonis</name></persName> rectoris
                        suprascripti ospitalis, de medietatem integram de omne ius et actione et
                        districtum quod eis pertinebat vel causare poterant per illam dationem quam
                            <rs key="#Consules">consules</rs> predicte civitatis eis fecerunt de
                        duabus petiis de terris que sunt canpi, in loco et finibus <placeName
                            ref="#places/3225">Debia</placeName>. Prima tenet unum caput in via
                        plubica et aliut in prato <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3212">Sancti
                            Salvatoris de <placeName ref="#places/3224"
                            >Cantignano</placeName></orgName>, latera anbo tenet in terra filiorum
                                <persName><name ref="Antonius">Antonii</name></persName>. Secunda
                        tenet unum caput in prato de Debia et aliut in media fossa ***, latus unum
                        in via publica et aliut in terra suprascriptorum filiorum quondam Antonii.
                        (â€¦) Et sub pena consulum et treuguanorum lucensium qui nunc sunt vel in
                        antea erunt. Unde ipsi germani receperunt exinde soldos quadraginta bonos
                        lucenses pro omnia suprascripta confirmanda. *** Insuper suprascripti
                        germani convenierunt et promiserunt suprascripto Ildebrando, si aliquo
                        tempore ipsi habuerint, libras quattuor lucensium denariorum, a consulibus
                        sive ab aliis personis pro quibus ipsi habent suprascriptas terras, quod
                        reddent eidem Ildebrando vel eius filio soldos viginti quinque sub
                        suprascripta pena. Hoc factum est <rs key="#Witness">presentia</rs>
                        <persName key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Ugierus"
                                >Ughieri</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Homodeus"
                                >Homodei</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Diportus"
                                >Diporti</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Iohannes"
                                >Iohannis</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Nuvilo"
                                >Nuviloni</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Beritius"
                                >Beriti</name></persName>. Anno dominice incarnationis millesimo
                        centesimo quinquagesimo secundo, sexto idus madii, indictione quintadecima.
                        Suprascripti homines ibi fuerunt. (L) <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name
                                ref="Heinricus">Henricus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> donni imperatoris omnibus his interfui et
                        memorie causa descripsi.</ab>
                </div>
